Thermite: metal powder and metal oxid (ofter aluminium)
exothermic reaction on ignition, high temperature
used in welding
MO + Al -> M + Al2O3 + heat

Sodium bicarbonate (E500)
Baking soda
Na+HCO3-
annual production 7Mt
white solid
production: Na2CO3 + CO2 + H2O -> 2 NaHCO3
thermal decomposition: 2 NaHCO3 -> Na2CO3 + H2O + CO2
antacid: NaHCO3 + HCl -> NaCl + H2O + CO
leavening agent: NaHCO3 + H+ -> Na+ + CO2 + H2O
odor remover, cleaning agent

Ammonia
NH3
annual production 150Mt
colourless gas, pungent smell
production
- Haber process (high pressure and temperature): N2 + 3 H2 -> 2 NH3
fertilizer production, fuel, coolant
product of amino acid deamination, converted to urea

Sodium carbonate (E500)
Washing soda
Na2CO3
white solid
production, Solvay process:
: NaCl + NH3 + CO2 + H2O -> NaHCO3 + NH4Cl
: 2NaHCO3 -> Na2CO3 + H2O + CO2
: 2NH4Cl + CaO -> 2NH3 + CaCl2 + H2O
cleansing agent, raising agent, glass manufacture

Calcium oxide
Quicklime
CaO
white solid
production: CaCO3 -> CaO + CO2 (temperature 900°C)
basic oxygen steelmaking, cement making, glass making

Calcium hydroxide (E526)
Ca(OH)2
acidity regulator
production: CaO + H2O -> Ca(OH)2

Calcium chloride (E509)
CaCl2
white crystalline solid
highly soluble in water
deicing agent (-50°C), dessicant (hygroscopic), dirt road dust control

Sulfuric acid
H2SO4
annual production 200Mt
colorless odorless liquid
highly corrosive
fertilizer production
exotermic hydration: H2SO4 + 2 H2O -> 2 H3O+ + SO4-
production, contact process:
: S + O2 -> SO2
: 2 SO2 + O2 -> 2 SO3 (catalyst V2O5)
: H2SO4 + SO3 -> H2S2O7
: H2S2O7 + H2O -> 2 H2SO4

Phosphoric acid
H3PO4
annual production 100Mt
colorless solid
